<i>Keep the party going</i>

1156
01:31:13,791 --> 01:31:16,458
<i>I'm prepared for what's to come, but...</i>

1157
01:31:16,541 --> 01:31:19,250
<i>Every last one of them's way too desperate</i>

1158
01:31:19,333 --> 01:31:23,791
<i>Looks likely my destiny'll get tied up,</i>
<i>too, so I brace for a different fate</i>

1159
01:31:24,458 --> 01:31:35,250
<i>I see myself in the rich colors</i>
<i>and briefness of the burning sunset</i>

1160
01:31:35,333 --> 01:31:40,083
<i>From the back of an unruly horse</i>

1161
01:31:40,166 --> 01:31:45,083
<i>The tail's to the east, which way is tomorrow?</i>

1162
