1175
01:33:14,125 --> 01:33:19,375
<i>Drunk on awakening, I can't stop</i>

1176
01:33:19,458 --> 01:33:24,708
<i>Last number one!! Don't hold back this time</i>

1177
01:33:24,791 --> 01:33:30,208
<i>Radiant enough to embrace the era</i>

1178
